{"tid":2118162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你當年放榜前一晚有咩搞？","createTime":"2020-07-21T09:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T12:54:54.000Z","uid":190827,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"041ad29ef2f97c47a504e668ddb5922b4b19d910","tid":2118162,"uid":190827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:50:14.000Z","msg":"我記得當年同成班同學出去公園飲酒<br />\n<br />\n玩到差唔多天光先返屋企換衫番學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身對自己成績都無咩期望所以完全無壓力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實想同聽日放榜嘅巴絲講，成績唔好唔洗死嘅<br />\n<br />\n係依一刻你可能覺得仆街了，點算<br />\n<br />\n但出黎做野後你會發現其實成績好唔好對你人生影響唔係真係咁大<br />\n<br />\n香港地你想讀U，真係有決心大把方法<br />\n<br />\n就算你唔讀都唔代表你死硬，當然條路可能會辛苦啲啦<br />\n<br />\n祝大家都有好成績<br />\n<br />\n利伸：未代AL 撚"},{"pid":"498e69422a4fa00dba9ae581f8e674f1be03ce77","tid":2118162,"uid":7332,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:54:36.000Z","msg":"同中學女朋友SMS左成晚,跟住第日特登著校服拎成績表,之後個成績入到U,同朋友坐係球場睇人打波"},{"pid":"ef071527b19024937402da06f914548726d8b280","tid":2118162,"uid":200266,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"同班fd睇世界盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲記得係法國對比利時"},{"pid":"61fad4234c5a015b0bd07c5b701dfdb65a4e3c67","tid":2118162,"uid":343361,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:57:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4592dda58430dd967ecb941eeb3f445ff95da6b6","tid":2118162,"uid":140145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9eedafe003fc79d4de5ada80494c2d17b43fa63","tid":2118162,"uid":201290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"普通嘅一日 嗰陣諗定retake<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5df21d88245008f16decb19ba7701784f79051","tid":2118162,"uid":190827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{